<div id="review_2214503657" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2214503657" />
    <a title="Lindsay - Traveling Sisters Book Reviews" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/54886546-lindsay---traveling-sisters-book-reviews"><img alt="Lindsay - Traveling Sisters Book Reviews" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1472552597p2/54886546.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2214503657?book_show_action=true">Apr 24, 2020</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Lindsay - Traveling Sisters Book Reviews" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Lindsay - Traveling Sisters Book Reviews" href="/user/show/54886546-lindsay---traveling-sisters-book-reviews">Lindsay - Traveling Sisters Book Reviews</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2214503657" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer12586176455517082258">4.5 exquisite stars!<br/><br/>There isn’t anything I could say about this book that hasn’t been said before. The writing is outstanding! It envelopes you within its beauty and holds you tight until the final sentence. I was intrigued by every single character. <br/><br/>This novel is a beautifully written, in-depth look at the connection between several families within one community. There are multiple characters, themes and storylines, each one adding a new layer of complexity and intrigue to the novel. I found my</span>
  <span id="freeText12586176455517082258" style="display:none">4.5 exquisite stars!<br /><br />There isn’t anything I could say about this book that hasn’t been said before. The writing is outstanding! It envelopes you within its beauty and holds you tight until the final sentence. I was intrigued by every single character. <br /><br />This novel is a beautifully written, in-depth look at the connection between several families within one community. There are multiple characters, themes and storylines, each one adding a new layer of complexity and intrigue to the novel. I found myself contemplating the decisions these characters made even when I didn’t have the book in my hands.<br /><br />Is it a fast-paced, gripping read? No. Is it highly suspenseful and addictive? No. Is it an exquisitely written exploration into the lives of endearing and unique characters that will leave you thinking of them long after you finish the book? Yes. Did it live up to the extreme hype? Yes!<br /><br />Long story short, if you haven’t read this novel (although I feel I might be the last person on earth who hadn’t read it by now), do yourself a favour and get your hands on a copy! Make sure to set aside quality time to spend between these pages as this story is one to be quietly savoured and cherished.</span>
  <a data-text-id="12586176455517082258" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


